data.description: Check out this awesome half-acre land! It's got a cool brick fence up front and it's all ready to build on – the place is cleared and flat. You can do whatever you want with it, whether it's your new home or a sweet business spot. And get this – it's in the fastest growing town in the whole US! Water, sewer and electricity available. Low Restrictions, you can bring your mobile home here too. Close to gas stations and stores. Close to Grand Parkway 99. Don't miss out on turning this space into your dreams. Grab it now and be part of the action!
